-- Merrill Lynch Unit to Offer Brokerage Services in Saudi Arabia
-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 2011-02-06T05:56:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-06/merrill-lynch-unit-to-offer-brokerage-services-in-saudi-arabia.html
  Bank of America Corp .’s Merrill Lynch
has been allowed to offer brokerage services in  Saudi Arabia 
through its unit in the country.  Merrill Lynch Kingdom of Saudi Arabia has become “a
licensed, approved and authorized member firm with the right to
conduct brokerage services and deal as principle and agent from
Feb. 6,” according to a statement on the Saudi bourse website
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  